<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 01:16:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>油价飙升引发通胀担忧，比特币走弱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-price-spike-revives-inflation-concerns</link><description>在美国对伊朗发动新的袭击后，油价飙升，比特币周一下跌，引发了人们对能源成本上升可能会重新带来通胀压力并抑制对风险资产的需求的担忧。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQM8fAzKiPzo/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 04:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-price-spike-revives-inflation-concerns</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 通过出售股票将储备金提高至 30 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/saylor-s-strategy-raises-reserve-to-3-billion-with-stock-sale</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 通过出售普通股筹集了约 4.67 亿美元，将其现金储备增加至约 30 亿美元，同时避免买卖比特币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3BHlXuTCKXI/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/saylor-s-strategy-raises-reserve-to-3-billion-with-stock-sale</guid></item><item><title>华尔街对万亿美元稳定币热潮发起阻力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/wall-street-mounts-pushback-on-trillion-dollar-stablecoin-boom</link><description>多年来，银行在很大程度上目睹了稳定币从一种利基加密货币产品发展成为每年交易量数十万亿美元的支付网络。现在，他们正在重新制定与 Zelle 相同的协作策略，押注共享基础设施是阻止数字美元进一步蚕食他们业务的最佳方式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8oewQVC2gFM/v9/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/wall-street-mounts-pushback-on-trillion-dollar-stablecoin-boom</guid></item></channel></rss>